00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:20,600
Han Li was straightforward,

579
00:28:20,600 --> 00:28:21,600
and blunt.

580
00:28:22,960 --> 00:28:24,280
Officer Zheng, as you know,

581
00:28:24,520 --> 00:28:26,040
finance workers

582
00:28:26,400 --> 00:28:28,640
rarely make friends easily.

583
00:28:29,080 --> 00:28:32,160
But there wasn't anyone

584
00:28:32,840 --> 00:28:33,640
she had issues with.

585
00:28:33,720 --> 00:28:35,400
How was her relationship
with the Director?

586
00:28:35,840 --> 00:28:36,800
Most business with the Director

587
00:28:36,800 --> 00:28:38,760
went through me directly.

588
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:40,680
She didn't interact

589
00:28:40,720 --> 00:28:41,560
with the Director very much.

590
00:28:44,040 --> 00:28:45,000
Sorry, I haven't offered you tea.

591
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:46,520
Here, let me.

592
00:28:46,520 --> 00:28:47,280
No, don't bother.

593
00:28:49,160 --> 00:28:50,560
Mr. Wang, are you okay?

594
00:28:51,040 --> 00:28:52,040
Let me take a look.

595
00:28:52,080 --> 00:28:52,800
It's nothing.

596
00:28:52,840 --> 00:28:53,400
A while back,

597
00:28:53,400 --> 00:28:55,200
I was out with the Director
for business.

598
00:28:55,360 --> 00:28:55,840
Let me see.

599
00:28:55,880 --> 00:28:56,880
They were drunk.

600
00:28:57,040 --> 00:28:58,640
There was a scuffle,

601
00:28:58,640 --> 00:28:59,360
see,

602
00:29:00,640 --> 00:29:02,760
and I got burned.

603
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:04,520
What's up with her teeth?

604
00:29:04,520 --> 00:29:06,920
The medical examiner said

605
00:29:07,520 --> 00:29:09,080
she bit the killer during the struggle.

606
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:10,640
My goodness.

607
00:29:10,640 --> 00:29:11,800
That's a nasty burn.

608
00:29:13,240 --> 00:29:16,400
Wang, you should let it breathe.

609
00:29:17,080 --> 00:29:19,120
Put some oil

610
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:21,040
or burn ointment on it.

611
00:29:22,240 --> 00:29:23,480
This is so bad.

612
00:29:23,600 --> 00:29:25,120
Your wife must be really worried.

613
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:28,160
Let me get you some tea.

614
00:29:28,200 --> 00:29:29,000
No, it's fine, Wang.

615
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:29,960
I'll be quick with my questions.

616
00:29:29,960 --> 00:29:30,880
Please, sit.

617
00:29:35,400 --> 00:29:37,720
Alright, Wang, let's get back to it.

618
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:41,000
Han Li didn't have any enemies.

619
00:29:41,440 --> 00:29:43,480
But did she have anyone
she was close to?

620
00:29:47,480 --> 00:29:49,440
I don't remember anyone in particular.

621
00:29:52,120 --> 00:29:53,560
