631
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:38,080
Your wife's face was covered in ink.

632
00:30:38,680 --> 00:30:39,640
See this mark here?

633
00:30:40,040 --> 00:30:40,840
Right?

634
00:30:51,480 --> 00:30:52,200
Wang,

635
00:30:52,560 --> 00:30:53,640
I know

636
00:30:53,640 --> 00:30:55,200
that to the outside world,

637
00:30:55,720 --> 00:30:59,600
you're seen as a good husband
and father.

638
00:31:00,240 --> 00:31:01,600
But was it

639
00:31:01,720 --> 00:31:03,440
Han Li's one-sided love

640
00:31:03,440 --> 00:31:04,120
