641
00:31:04,120 --> 00:31:05,760
We had no improper relationship.

642
00:31:06,920 --> 00:31:09,160
So you were aware she liked you?

643
00:31:20,720 --> 00:31:23,600
I pretended not to know.

644
00:31:24,840 --> 00:31:26,240
I didn't want things to become awkward

645
00:31:26,240 --> 00:31:27,960
at work.

646
00:31:34,240 --> 00:31:35,800
I feel sorry

647
00:31:37,200 --> 00:31:38,120
