650
00:31:45,520 --> 00:31:47,160
We worked together for so many years.

651
00:31:48,160 --> 00:31:49,360
I want her

652
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:51,360
to rest in peace.

653
00:31:54,800 --> 00:31:55,600
Enough.

654
00:31:56,480 --> 00:31:57,240
Yao and I

655
00:31:57,240 --> 00:31:59,080
asked every house

656
00:31:59,320 --> 00:32:00,320
along Han Li's route home.

657
00:32:01,240 --> 00:32:02,600
Whether it was the kebab sellers

658
00:32:02,600 --> 00:32:04,520
