660
00:32:05,760 --> 00:32:06,960
No one saw her.

661
00:32:07,240 --> 00:32:08,240
It's strange.

662
00:32:08,760 --> 00:32:09,840
Didn't she go home

663
00:32:09,840 --> 00:32:11,000
after work?

664
00:32:12,320 --> 00:32:13,120
Guozhu,

665
00:32:13,560 --> 00:32:16,800
