666
00:32:17,200 --> 00:32:18,920
The full autopsy report
will be out tomorrow,

667
00:32:19,440 --> 00:32:20,360
but the medical examiner said

668
00:32:20,360 --> 00:32:22,040
the body had been in the water too long.

669
00:32:22,120 --> 00:32:23,440
Whatever evidence there was

670
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:24,320
might have been washed away.

671
00:32:26,040 --> 00:32:26,760
What about the lethal weapon?

672
00:32:26,760 --> 00:32:28,040
It's almost certain.

673
00:32:28,880 --> 00:32:29,680
An entrenching tool.

674
00:32:30,080 --> 00:32:31,600
The blunt force trauma on the body

675
00:32:31,640 --> 00:32:32,720
