676
00:32:32,720 --> 00:32:34,240
are both caused by the entrenching tool.

677
00:32:34,920 --> 00:32:37,320
The wounds on the body are rough.

678
00:32:38,000 --> 00:32:39,760
At first, I thought it was an axe,

679
00:32:39,800 --> 00:32:41,000
