of a motive for murder.

726
00:34:21,360 --> 00:34:24,040
Until we figure out
the primary crime scene,

727
00:34:24,240 --> 00:34:26,000
who the killer is remains unknown.

728
00:34:26,440 --> 00:34:27,520
We should move quickly.

729
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:29,960
Since Wang Jianmin is the only clue
that we have,

730
00:34:30,280 --> 00:34:32,320
let's track all his movements

731
00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:33,760
on the day Han Li disappeared.

732
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:35,360
If he's innocent,

733
00:34:35,600 --> 00:34:37,680
we can rule him out.

734
00:34:39,120 --> 00:34:40,280
Wang Jianmin has a car,

735
00:34:40,640 --> 00:34:41,760
so,

736
00:34:41,760 --> 00:34:42,560
he'll be easier to trace.

737
00:34:43,280 --> 00:34:44,080
Let's get to it.

738
00:34:44,280 --> 00:34:45,080
Okay. No problem.

739
00:34:47,920 --> 00:34:48,720
Excuse me, sir,

740
00:34:49,120 --> 00:34:50,840
you set up your stall here
every day, right?

741
00:34:51,160 --> 00:34:52,520
What's going on, madam?

742
00:34:52,720 --> 00:34:53,680
You're banning me?

743
00:34:53,880 --> 00:34:55,360
I've been here for years.

744
00:34:55,400 --> 00:34:56,680
I've never heard of any restrictions.

745
00:34:56,680 --> 00:34:58,080
No, relax.

746
00:34:58,200 --> 00:34:59,240
Nothing like that.

747
00:34:59,240 --> 00:35:01,000
Just wanted to ask

748
00:35:01,360 --> 00:35:03,280
if you saw this car on Tuesday night.

749
00:35:04,760 --> 00:35:06,280
With all the cars coming and going,

750
00:35:06,440 --> 00:35:08,200
how could I remember this one?

751
00:35:08,320 --> 00:35:09,440
What about the driver?

752
00:35:09,440 --> 00:35:11,280
Does he look familiar?

753
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:16,200
Actually, yeah, I do remember him.

754
00:35:16,680 --> 00:35:17,360
Really?

755
00:35:17,360 --> 00:35:18,280
Yeah.

756
00:35:19,000 --> 00:35:20,120
That night,

757
00:35:20,200 --> 00:35:21,080
it was so hot,

758
00:35:21,160 --> 00:35:22,200
not many passengers on the street.

759
00:35:22,200 --> 00:35:23,520
So I was packing up early to head home.

760
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:46,200
He was very polite to me,

761
00:35:46,440 --> 00:35:47,560
so I remembered him.

762
00:35:52,920 --> 00:35:54,600
Thanks to the vendor's information,

763
00:35:55,000 --> 00:35:56,960
we've pinpointed the crime scene.

764
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:04,240
Did you see this person

765
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:05,440
in the afternoon of 3rd April?

766
00:36:05,680 --> 00:36:06,480
No, I didn't.

767
00:36:06,720 --> 00:36:07,280
Think carefully.

768
00:36:07,280 --> 00:36:08,120
About this tall.

769
00:36:09,840 --> 00:36:10,880
What about this car?

770
00:36:12,680 --> 00:36:13,600
White.

771
00:36:15,040 --> 00:36:15,880
No, haven't seen it.

772
00:36:16,720 --> 00:36:18,480
Not around this street?

773
00:36:44,120 --> 00:36:45,640
No wonder our earlier searches

774
00:36:45,640 --> 00:36:46,560
turned up nothing.

775
00:36:46,640 --> 00:36:49,000
It's in the opposite direction
of Han Li's home.

776
00:36:51,960 --> 00:36:54,280
If I were planning a murder or attack,

777
00:36:55,120 --> 00:36:57,160
I'd choose a secluded spot.

778
00:36:58,200 --> 00:36:59,840
This place is right in front
