785
00:37:09,720 --> 00:37:10,600
He's definitely not crazy.

786
00:37:10,800 --> 00:37:11,360
Yeah.

787
00:37:12,120 --> 00:37:13,480
So why would he choose here?

788
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:15,840
Tell Guozhu

789
00:37:15,880 --> 00:37:17,480
to send the blood to the station.

790
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:20,200
After analysis,

791
00:37:20,240 --> 00:37:22,960
