is confirmed to be Han Li's.

792
00:37:35,680 --> 00:37:37,600
Don't you think
he has a split personality?

793
00:37:38,640 --> 00:37:40,000
On the one hand,

794
00:37:40,160 --> 00:37:40,920
he's silly enough to murder

795
00:37:40,920 --> 00:37:42,480
so close to the police station.

796
00:37:43,600 --> 00:37:45,080
But on the other hand,

797
00:37:45,080 --> 00:37:46,560
he's cautious enough

798
00:37:46,680 --> 00:37:48,280
to dump the body somewhere else.

799
00:37:51,720 --> 00:37:53,920
Scholars are better with their pens
than their hands.

800
00:37:54,480 --> 00:37:56,800
If you told me to drag a body that far,

801
00:37:57,760 --> 00:37:58,880
I couldn't do it.

802
00:38:01,160 --> 00:38:02,840
The Xianfeng Road police station

803
00:38:02,840 --> 00:38:05,120
