804
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:06,640
Even if the body were found there,

805
00:38:06,640 --> 00:38:08,080
no one would suspect him.

806
00:38:08,880 --> 00:38:10,480
No matter what his motive is,

807
00:38:10,480 --> 00:38:11,920
the hospital confirmed one thing.

808
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:13,400
He stayed in the hospital,

809
00:38:13,400 --> 00:38:14,800
but his left hand wasn't injured at all.

810
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:16,800
If he didn't have anything to hide,
why did he lie?

811
00:38:17,040 --> 00:38:18,480
We should just bring him in.

812
00:38:18,520 --> 00:38:19,600
Interrogate him,
and we'll know everything.

813
00:38:26,520 --> 00:38:28,000
When we were interviewing people
at Yunhui Pharma,

814
00:38:28,640 --> 00:38:29,920
one of Han Li's coworkers mentioned

815
00:38:30,600 --> 00:38:32,400
she photocopied a financial ledger

816
00:38:33,040 --> 00:38:34,600
just before leaving that day.

817
00:38:35,240 --> 00:38:36,920
The coworker saw it from a distance,
and didn't think much of it.

818
00:38:37,680 --> 00:38:38,440
At the time,

819
00:38:38,440 --> 00:38:40,160
we also assumed

820
00:38:40,760 --> 00:38:41,680
it was just routine finance work.

821
00:38:42,480 --> 00:38:43,560
But now that I think about it.

822
00:38:45,360 --> 00:38:46,640
What if it wasn't that simple?

823
00:39:01,200 --> 00:39:02,080
Look,

824
00:39:02,640 --> 00:39:04,920
the Xianfeng Road police station

825
00:39:05,240 --> 00:39:07,240
is the nearest one
to the pharmaceutical company,

826
00:39:07,680 --> 00:39:09,040
and Han Li's home

827
00:39:09,240 --> 00:39:10,640
isn't in that direction.

828
00:39:11,600 --> 00:39:12,640
Is it possible

829
00:39:12,640 --> 00:39:15,520
that Han Li was planning
to report to the police that day?

830
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:17,800
Maybe Wang Jianmin had no choice

831
00:39:17,880 --> 00:39:19,440
but to act there.

832
00:39:22,480 --> 00:39:23,960
Our joint investigation
with the major crimes unit

833
00:39:24,520 --> 00:39:25,720
was because we suspected Yunhui Pharma

834
00:39:25,720 --> 00:39:27,000
might be involved
in drug-related activity.

835
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:29,240
Han Li probably found something wrong,

836
00:39:29,480 --> 00:39:31,240
and the ledger she copied
could be the evidence.

837
00:39:31,840 --> 00:39:33,120
Maybe Wang Jianmin silenced her

838
00:39:33,120 --> 00:39:34,720
to destroy that evidence.

839
00:39:35,280 --> 00:39:36,840
If that's the case,

840
00:39:36,840 --> 00:39:38,480
everything makes sense.

841
00:39:40,600 --> 00:39:43,840
We'll have a word with Wang Jianmin.

